  "synopsis": "The plot revolves around Kaoru Torigara, only son of a ramen shop owner, who is going to renovate his inherited ramen shop. He discovers that his shop has a guardian angel named Pretty Menma. Pretty Menma tells Kaoru that his dead father's intention is making him succeed in the \"Food King Wars\", a battle of restaurants around the world that is held every 4 years. Kaoru and Menma must help each other to go through the struggles of the \"Food King Wars\".\n\n(Source: Wikipedia)",
